                        <h4><i class="fas fa-building"></i> <span data-translate="faq_q1">Are you a factory, or a trading company?</span></h4>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p data-translate="faq_a1_1">We are the <strong>factory directly</strong>. Established in 2003, we are a certified manufacturer with over 20 years of experience in non-woven products manufacturing.</p>
                        <p data-translate="faq_a1_2">We are authorized by Chinese law to conduct import and export business, which means you work directly with the source, ensuring:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a1_3">Better pricing without middleman markup</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a1_4">Direct quality control from production line</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a1_5">Faster communication and decision-making</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a1_6">Full transparency in manufacturing process</li>
                        </ul>
