                            <li data-translate="faq_a2_4"><strong>Custom Branding:</strong> Logo printing on mask outer layer (any color as required)</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a2_5"><strong>Packaging Customization:</strong> Individual, retail, and bulk packaging options</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a2_6"><strong>Product Range:</strong> Adult, teen, and kids sizes; 2-4 layer options</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> <span data-translate="faq_q3">What's your production capacity?</span></h4>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
