                            <li data-translate="faq_a3_3"><strong>Production Lines:</strong> 15 fully automated lines</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a3_4"><strong>Factory Area:</strong> 100,000 square meters with 3 modern buildings</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a3_5"><strong>Clean Room:</strong> 100,000-class ISO-certified environment</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a3_6"><strong>Scalability:</strong> Can increase capacity based on order requirements</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-medal"></i> <span data-translate="faq_q4">What are your competitive advantages?</span></h4>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p data-translate="faq_a4_1">We differentiate ourselves through three key advantages:</p>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a4_2"><strong>1. Certified Manufacturing Excellence</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_3">Chinese government-licensed medical device manufacturer</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_4">Class 2 medical device registration for disposable masks</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_5">CE and FDA certifications completed for EU and US markets</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_6">ISO 9001:2015 quality management system certified</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a4_7"><strong>2. Unparalleled Geographic Advantage</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_8">Located in Xiantao - world's largest non-woven protective equipment production base</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_9">China's only national non-woven production promotion center</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_10">National emergency medical protective material production and storage base</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_11">Complete industrial chain integration from raw materials to finished products</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a4_12"><strong>3. 20+ Years of Manufacturing Expertise</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_13">Established in 2003 with continuous operation since</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_14">One of the largest mask exporters to Japan (known for stringent quality standards)</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_15">Deep understanding of every detail in the supply chain</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a4_16">Proven track record with international clients</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-plane-departure"></i> <span data-translate="faq_q5">Can we visit your factory?</span></h4>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
