                        <p data-translate="faq_a5_1"><strong>Absolutely! We warmly welcome business visits to our factory.</strong></p>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a5_2"><strong>Factory Address:</strong><br>
                        No.72, Textile Industrial Park, Yuanshi Avenue, Xiantao City, Hubei Province, China</p>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a5_3"><strong>Location Advantage:</strong><br>
                        Our facility is conveniently located just 110km from Wuhan - the provincial capital and largest transportation hub in central China.</p>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a5_4"><strong>Travel Options:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a5_5"><strong>By Air:</strong> Fly directly to Wuhan Tianhe International Airport (WUH)</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a5_6"><strong>By Train:</strong> Take high-speed rail to Wuhan Railway Station or Hankou Railway Station, or even nearer: Xiantaoxi Railway Station or Tianmennan Railway Station</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a5_7"><strong>Ground Transportation:</strong> We arrange all onward travel from Wuhan to our factory</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a5_8"><strong>Visit Arrangements:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a5_9">Factory tour of production lines and quality control facilities</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a5_10">Meeting with technical and management teams</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a5_11">Sample inspection and testing demonstration</li>
                            <li data-translate="faq_a5_12">Lunch and local transportation arrangements</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a5_13"><strong>Virtual Alternative:</strong><br>
                        If travel is not convenient, we offer comprehensive virtual factory tours via video conference with live demonstrations and Q&A sessions.</p>
                        
                        <p data-translate="faq_a5_14"><strong>To Schedule:</strong> Please contact our sales manager or use the inquiry form above to arrange your visit.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
